      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "But they were their all - their living, their home; and, forsaking them, they had as really shown their sincerity as though they had possessed the gold of Ophir and lived in the palaces of kings.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "What shall we have, therefore? - We have done as thou didst command this young man to do. What reward may we expect for it?",
